data.description: Exquisite 2460 sq. ft. new house with 4 Bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms nestled on 7.65 acres of exceptional land with a mature tree line for privacy behind a breathtaking custom entry gate!  Only 2 minutes to Hwy. 74 bypass for commuting to Charlotte, Gastonia or Shelby, or an escape to the mountains. Stunning acreage that could easily be subdivided to accommodate 3 more homes. There are lots of upgrades: Custom kitchen, custom cafe appliances, quartz countertops throughout, LVP throughout, fireplace, additional cement drive and patio, 12x12 cement dog kennel, HD video cameras, security alarm package, cedar shutters and entry columns, 20 Italian cypresses, Tennessee River rock, Thuja giant evergreens, screened back porch, large garage with storage closet and access door, solid custom mahogany entry door, shiplap to vaulted ceiling, bricked mailbox with house plaque, fenced back yard and so many more upgrades not listed.  Showing to begin Saturday April 20.
